('95211','32840','5','House with pool in 1st sea line in El Toro'),
('95212','32841','5','El Toro is located in the municipality of Calvia in south west Mallorca. This residencial villagedoes not only offer a year-round functioning infrastructure with supermarkets and restaurants, but also the popular marina Port Adriano, with its famous restaurants and designer boutiques. In the immediate vicinity, the golfers will get their costs. 4 golf courses to choose from.\r\nThe house was built in 1995 on a 630m² large, south-west facing sea view plot. The 220m² living space spreads over 2 floors plus a fitness room in the basement. On the ground floor is the entrance with entrance hall, living-dining room with fireplace, kitchen with utility room, 1 bathroom and a garage with space for 1 car: Upstairs are the master bedroom with dressing room, 3 bedrooms, 1 bathroom and a terrace. Outside you´ll find a swimming pool and a mediterranean garden with several terraces. Facilities include a oil central heating, PVC double glazed windows and air conditioning h/c\r\n'),
